title: One By One
lyrics:
I don't know why
I've spent a lifetime
Searching for what's mine
When you're already here
By my side

Kept building my fences

Wasting my chances

Help me find

Way back home



My heart is a mess now

Need to confess now

Kept fooling myself

Lost my sight



But now I can see you

Sun's shining with you

Dark days are gone

One by one
